{"tid":2169262,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"trump:若中國盼我勝選 是對我的侮辱","createTime":"2020-08-22T10:54:32.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-22T11:03:29.000Z","uid":75656,"like":29,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"ad1931120ad2fd1b6076c6fb19a6419f9bd00034","tid":2169262,"uid":75656,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-22T10:54:32.000Z","msg":"美國民主黨完成提名程序，由前副總統拜登挑戰現任總統川普，眼見對手來勢洶洶，川普的火力也逐漸加大，強調若是拜登當選，中國就能夠把持美國，還稱若是他被中國寄望勝選，對他來說是一種侮辱。<br />\n<br />\n川普當地時間週五在2020年國家政策委員會會議上表示，「是時候拒絕民主黨帶來的憤怒和仇恨，我們將迎來此生最重大的選舉，沒有政黨能夠花費那麼長的時間撕裂美國。」<br />\n<br />\n川普批評，拜登在民主黨全代會上講得口沫橫飛，卻沒有提到法律的執行及如何為城市帶來安全，尤其是那些在民主黨主政下完全失控的城市，也沒有對中國議題有任何形式的表態，「如果拜登當選，中國將會把持我們的國家，<span class=\"red\">你們都看過了情報機構的報告，中國非常想要拜登勝選，如果他們希望我贏，對我來說就是一種侮辱</span>。」<br />\n<br />\n美國情報機構先前發布報告，指中國認為川普難以預測，希望他連任失敗，亦即較支持拜登勝出。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3267946\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3267946&d=aFiO92UEzPWfS5u3FViI6Q5Iyec62GFiithg4eFnous%3D&h=f6eaf2db\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3267946&h=3385e9e9\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3267946</a>"},{"pid":"8fb0ef968c4e2adab5936bc84b6330bf2f71e165","tid":2169262,"uid":61280,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-22T10:56:34.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\"><span class=\"red\"><span class=\"red\"><span class=\"xx-large\"><strong>一句封喉，完美！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></strong></span></span></span></span></span>"},{"pid":"595782d1e8fe173df8962ef28d9fa39f3e4cfcaa","tid":2169262,"uid":343361,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-22T10:58:42.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f7ff12524f3b1e5a7517454a749c776429305eb3","tid":2169262,"uid":11809,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-22T11:01:08.000Z","msg":"型撚到<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e87494aa731c73bbc178cc6c103661c497854fa9","tid":2169262,"uid":39012,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-22T11:03:29.000Z","msg":"通常應該係後邊係接 本來我是想大聲斥責的 但錢實在是太多了<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}